-LRB- Federal deposit insurance would pay principal and interest accrued to the date of liquidation , to a maximum of $ 100,000 . -RRB-
`` <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">It</COREF> 's not a blanket commitment , <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> 's a case - by - case situation , '' says Albert Disposti , a managing director of <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">Merrill Lynch Money Markets Inc</COREF> .
